Targets are as follows:

54
00:05:53,008 --> 00:05:57,008
The Demon of Sound: Nerissa Ravencroft

55
00:05:57,508 --> 00:06:02,008
The Jewel of Emotions: Koseki Bijou

56
00:06:02,008 --> 00:06:06,008
The Fluffy One: Fuwawa Abyssguard

57
00:06:06,008 --> 00:06:10,008
The Fuzzy One: Mococo Abyssguard

58
00:06:10,008 --> 00:06:14,508
The Archiver: Shiori Novella

59
00:06:15,008 --> 00:06:18,008
All units, apprehend the Advent members immediately.

60
00:06:25,008 --> 00:06:28,008
Oh my god! Holy... We're in trouble!

61
00:06:28,008 --> 00:06:31,008
It's the B-word! Run!

62
00:06:31,008 --> 00:06:34,008
Oh my god! They're catching us!

63
00:06:47,008 --> 00:06:50,008
Hey! Be careful!

64
00:06:50,008 --> 00:06:55,008
Oh no! They're so close! What are we doing?!

65
00:06:58,008 --> 00:07:00,508
Think, there's got to be a solution for this, right?

66
00:07:01,008 --> 00:07:03,508
Piggyback ride! Come on!

67
00:07:08,508 --> 00:07:11,008
Okay, maybe not that one.

68
00:07:12,508 --> 00:07:15,508
There has to be something though, plan B...

69
00:07:16,008 --> 00:07:19,508
Bwahaha! Struggling already?

70
00:07:22,008 --> 00:07:24,008
What are you doing here?

71
00:07:24,008 --> 00:07:26,008
Finally show your face, huh?

72
00:07:26,008 --> 00:07:28,508
Ask nicely enough, and maybe I'll save your skins.

73
00:07:29,008 --> 00:07:32,008
I'll punch you for a "mlem". Come on, come on!

74
00:07:32,508 --> 00:07:34,508
Um, here, I have a solution.

75
00:07:34,508 --> 00:07:37,008
Oh! Whoa! Don't race us so fast, Pokey!

76
00:07:40,008 --> 00:07:42,008
Hmph! I don't hate that.

77
00:07:42,508 --> 00:07:45,008
If you manage to pass the little trial I've cooked up,

78
00:07:45,008 --> 00:07:47,508
I'll whisk you away to a whole other realm...

79
00:07:48,008 --> 00:07:50,508
One where your pesky pursuers can't reach you!

80
00:07:51,008 --> 00:07:53,008
I mean, I guess that's our only option, huh?

81
00:07:53,008 --> 00:07:55,008
I guess so. Oh well, guess we will do it.

82
00:07:56,008 --> 00:08:00,008
Alright. I've prepared something special. Arise!

83
00:08:01,008 --> 00:08:04,008
Go-Kart Escape (逃走ゴーカート)
Go-Kart Escape

84
00:08:07,508 --> 00:08:09,508
What if you don't have a license?

85
00:08:10,008 --> 00:08:12,508
Why... What's with all the Biboo-themed stuff?

86
00:08:12,508 --> 00:08:14,008
Interesting choice. Why do I like that?

87
00:08:15,008 --> 00:08:17,508
See this course? Time to tackle the

88
00:08:17,508 --> 00:08:19,508
"Go-Kart Escape Challenge"!

89
00:08:20,008 --> 00:08:23,008
Oh my god! Escape! Escaping! Okay!

90
00:08:24,008 --> 00:08:26,508
Yes, that's right. Take it from here, ankle-biter.

91
00:08:27,008 --> 00:08:30,008
Hey! Who are you talking to, huh?

92
00:08:30,008 --> 00:08:33,008
Who you calling ankle-biter? Hey! Settle down.

93
00:08:33,508 --> 00:08:36,008
Actually, all right team, game rules are incoming,

94
00:08:36,008 --> 00:08:38,008
so make sure you better listen, okay?

95
00:08:39,008 --> 00:08:43,008
Wait, what's that? Shiori, Shiori, can you...?

96
00:08:44,008 --> 00:08:46,508
Yeah! Oh, nice!

97
00:08:47,008 --> 00:08:50,008
Wait, Bijou, how do you know the game rules?

98
00:08:51,008 --> 00:08:54,008
It's the glasses. That's how she knows. Yeah!

99
00:08:55,008 --> 00:09:00,008
Rule 1: Survive 2 laps with zombies on your tail!

100
00:09:00,008 --> 00:09:02,508
Zombies? Zombies?! Where? Where?

101
00:09:02,508 --> 00:09:05,008
Remember last year we beat up zombies?

102
00:09:05,508 --> 00:09:09,008
Well, one of them went on a path to revenge...

103
00:09:09,008 --> 00:09:13,008
and now it's gonna run after you.

104
00:09:13,008 --> 00:09:15,508
Oh, okay. Run! Oh no!

105
00:09:16,008 --> 00:09:19,008
Rule 2: Collect items for bonus points,

106
00:09:19,008 --> 00:09:22,008
but watch out for traps that deduct points!

107
00:09:22,508 --> 00:09:26,508
Oh no! Points? What the... points?

108
00:09:27,008 --> 00:09:30,008
Rule 3: Victory is ours if we all get

109
00:09:30,008 --> 00:09:32,008
30 points total! Easy, right?

110
00:09:32,508 --> 00:09:35,008
30 points?! Did you hear that?

111
00:09:35,008 --> 00:09:37,008
30 points! Oh yeah, we can do that.

112
00:09:38,008 --> 00:09:41,008
All right, I will explain the course items...

113
00:09:41,508 --> 00:09:44,508
I must run. You must run? Yeah, she must run.

114
00:09:45,008 --> 00:09:47,508
I'm gonna live out my dreams while

115
00:09:47,508 --> 00:09:50,008
there's a track! Just explain, ignore me!

116
00:09:50,008 --> 00:09:53,008
Okay! So listening! Uh... Oh, she's fast.

117
00:09:54,008 --> 00:09:57,008
Anyway, there are crystals on the field.

118
00:09:57,008 --> 00:09:59,008
It's the Biboo crystal over there. And...

119
00:10:00,016 --> 00:10:01,816
And two more over there! They are gacha.

120
00:10:02,016 --> 00:10:04,516
Oh, you either gain points or lose points...

121
00:10:04,516 --> 00:10:07,516
...but you don't know, so it's a risk every time!

122
00:10:07,516 --> 00:10:10,516
Gacha! Yeah! And then...

123
00:10:10,516 --> 00:10:13,516
...there is the big Moai! The big Moai!

124
00:10:17,516 --> 00:10:20,016
It will block your path. Oh! Whoa! Hi!

125
00:10:22,016 --> 00:10:25,016
It is minus 20 points if you hit it...

126
00:10:25,016 --> 00:10:28,516
...so don't hit it. Or hit it if you want.

127
00:10:29,016 --> 00:10:32,016
Yeah, don't hit it! And then, the Pebble!

128
00:10:32,016 --> 00:10:34,516
Look at the Pebble! I have...

129
00:10:34,516 --> 00:10:37,516
...kidnapped one of my Pebbles...

130
00:10:37,516 --> 00:10:41,016
...to use as a sacrifice. If you hit it...

131
00:10:41,016 --> 00:10:44,016
...minus 5 points. But you know what...

132
00:10:44,016 --> 00:10:47,516
...I don't think they would mind if you hit it.

133
00:10:48,016 --> 00:10:51,016
To be honest. Okay, yeah!

134
00:10:51,516 --> 00:10:54,516
And the items will change depending on...

135
00:10:54,516 --> 00:10:57,016
...your first lap or second lap.

136
00:10:57,016 --> 00:10:59,016
You're doing two laps. Two laps! Okay!

137
00:11:00,016 --> 00:11:03,016
By the way, too many! You can run another laps?

138
00:11:03,016 --> 00:11:05,516
Yeah! Are you okay? Yeah, I'm great!

139
00:11:06,516 --> 00:11:09,516
I guess time to show you how it's done.

140
00:11:09,516 --> 00:11:12,516
Sure, go on, go on! Alright, first lap!

141
00:11:13,016 --> 00:11:15,516
Show us how to do it! I'm ready!

142
00:11:17,516 --> 00:11:21,016
3... 2... 1... GO!

143
00:11:21,516 --> 00:11:24,016
Go! You're so fast! Oh, first lap!

144
00:11:24,516 --> 00:11:27,516
She gets a crystal, she makes a loop!

145
00:11:28,016 --> 00:11:31,016
Second crystal! Watch out, watch out!

146
00:11:31,516 --> 00:11:34,516
She's going so fast! Zombie's speeding up!

147
00:11:36,016 --> 00:11:39,016
Second lap, let's go! Another crystal!

148
00:11:39,516 --> 00:11:42,516
She hit another one! Moai! The zombie!

149
00:11:43,516 --> 00:11:47,016
Go, go, go, go, go! The zombie is speeding up!

150
00:11:48,016 --> 00:11:51,516
The crystal at the end... minus 3 pt. Yeah!

151
00:11:58,516 --> 00:12:01,016
I think you got a bit of bad luck...

152
00:12:01,016 --> 00:12:03,516
...with that crystal at the end.

153
00:12:04,516 --> 00:12:07,516
It's okay, that was a pretty good run.

154
00:12:07,516 --> 00:12:10,516
You went so fast! You almost hit the zombie...

155
00:12:10,516 --> 00:12:14,016
...but you're okay! Yeah, you didn't die!

156
00:12:14,516 --> 00:12:17,016
How many points did I get? How many points?

157
00:12:18,016 --> 00:12:21,016
That's a good question. How many points...

158
00:12:21,016 --> 00:12:24,016
...did you get? I think you got one point.

159
00:12:24,016 --> 00:12:27,016
What? One point? Oh, wasn't that negative?

160
00:12:27,016 --> 00:12:30,016
Did I have bad gacha luck? It's okay.

161
00:12:30,016 --> 00:12:33,016
It's a group effort, we can still get points.

162
00:12:34,016 --> 00:12:36,516
Yeah, I contributed one! One is great!

163
00:12:37,016 --> 00:12:40,016
We'll let the pro do all the work for you, right?

164
00:12:40,516 --> 00:12:43,516
Yeah, yeah! Pro Mococo! Yeah, yeah!

165
00:12:44,016 --> 00:12:47,516
I'm counting on you guys! Okay!

166
00:12:47,516 --> 00:12:50,516
Next up is... Shiori! Show us how it's done!

167
00:12:50,516 --> 00:12:53,016
Our fearless leader! I have a plan.

168
00:12:53,016 --> 00:12:56,016
You have a plan? What's your plan?

169
00:12:56,016 --> 00:12:59,016
You'll figure it out when I say 'Plan'.

170
00:12:59,016 --> 00:13:01,016
Okay, good luck, Shiori! Shiori!

171
00:13:01,516 --> 00:13:04,516
あの、あの、ゾンビら... 先どうぞ？
Um, um, zombies... go ahead?

172
00:13:04,516 --> 00:13:08,016
え？ 何？ はい。 行こうですね、行こうですね。
Eh? What? Yes. Let's go, let's go.

173
00:13:09,016 --> 00:13:12,016
You got this! 3... 2... 1...

174
00:13:13,516 --> 00:13:16,516
Let's go! GO! Let's go! You're so...

175
00:13:17,516 --> 00:13:20,516
Yeah, that's like a... no! Come on, let's go!

176
00:13:21,016 --> 00:13:24,516
Oh! Crystal... minus 1 pt. Touch me! Hit me!

177
00:13:24,516 --> 00:13:27,516
Watch me! Watch me! Watch me! Moai!

178
00:13:28,016 --> 00:13:31,516
No, no, no, no! Yeah, the zombie! Go, go, go!

179
00:13:32,016 --> 00:13:34,516
Yeah, yeah, yeah! Look at her go!

180
00:13:34,516 --> 00:13:37,516
She's like driving in New York!

181
00:13:37,516 --> 00:13:40,016
Only taking points! That's okay.

182
00:13:40,016 --> 00:13:42,516
I can figure it out. How many points did she...

183
00:13:43,016 --> 00:13:46,016
Oh! Watch out! Okay, okay, okay!

184
00:13:46,516 --> 00:13:49,016
You can't figure it out... oh! No!

185
00:13:49,016 --> 00:13:52,516
Minus 3 pt. You didn't catch him...

186
00:13:53,016 --> 00:13:56,516
...but you sure gave him a run for his money.

187
00:13:56,516 --> 00:14:00,016
Look at that driving! It's not about the points.

188
00:14:00,016 --> 00:14:03,016
I just wanted to run them over. Understandable.

189
00:14:04,016 --> 00:14:07,016
It's okay, how many points did I get?

190
00:14:07,016 --> 00:14:09,516
Let's see... Three points! Oh, three points!

191
00:14:10,516 --> 00:14:13,016
That's two more points than Bijou!

192
00:14:13,516 --> 00:14:16,516
No, that's pretty good. Better than one!

193
00:14:17,016 --> 00:14:20,016
So we have four! Alright, it's up to Fuwa...

194
00:14:20,016 --> 00:14:23,016
...do you think you can do it?

195
00:14:23,016 --> 00:14:26,516
I'll get four more points! You can do it!

196
00:14:26,516 --> 00:14:30,016
I know you can! Yeah! I'm gonna tell you...

197
00:14:30,516 --> 00:14:34,016
...the zombie is not gonna run away anymore.

198
00:14:34,516 --> 00:14:37,516
I think it's tired. It's up to you!

199
00:14:37,516 --> 00:14:40,516
You gotta outrun it! I'm the best driver! Yeah!

200
00:14:40,516 --> 00:14:43,516
Go, Fuwa, go! 3... 2... 1... GO!

201
00:14:44,016 --> 00:14:47,016
Go! Let's go, Fuwawa! Oh no, you're going slow!

202
00:14:48,016 --> 00:14:51,516
What do you mean? I want to go faster!

203
00:14:52,016 --> 00:14:55,016
This is very safe driving! Yeah, yeah!

204
00:14:55,516 --> 00:14:59,016
You missed the crystal! It's okay...

205
00:14:59,016 --> 00:14:59,516
...the zombie's taking its time too!

206
00:15:00,024 --> 00:15:00,924
It's already start!

207
00:15:00,924 --> 00:15:02,324
Wait, I have to go!

208
00:15:02,324 --> 00:15:04,124
Okay, baby!

209
00:15:04,124 --> 00:15:05,124
Yeah!

210
00:15:05,124 --> 00:15:05,924
Oh, no!

211
00:15:05,924 --> 00:15:07,424
Oh, the zombie!

212
00:15:07,424 --> 00:15:09,124
My crystal!

213
00:15:09,124 --> 00:15:10,524
It's okay, it's okay.

214
00:15:10,524 --> 00:15:13,224
Go, go, go, go, go, go, go!

215
00:15:13,224 --> 00:15:16,424
