みんな！ここだよ！ここにいるよ！
Guys! We're here! We're here!

703
00:44:51,064 --> 00:44:53,564
声は聞こえるけど、姿が見えないよ！
I hear your voice, but I do not see a body!

704
00:44:53,864 --> 00:44:55,564
みんな、待って待って！下を見て！
Guys, wait, wait, wait! Look down!

705
00:44:58,564 --> 00:45:00,064
バウバウ！
Bau Bau!

706
00:45:00,512 --> 00:45:02,212
Oh, they're so cute! Wait a second...

707
00:45:02,212 --> 00:45:03,112
Yeah...

708
00:45:03,512 --> 00:45:07,312
Wait, those voices coming from... from the dogs?

709
00:45:07,512 --> 00:45:09,912
I think this might be FuwaMoco!

710
00:45:10,112 --> 00:45:13,912
What? Wait, Nerissa! FuwaMoco have been turned...

711
00:45:13,912 --> 00:45:15,612
...into Dobermans?!

712
00:45:15,612 --> 00:45:17,612
Oh my god! Are you guys okay?

713
00:45:17,712 --> 00:45:20,712
Yeah, you know, I think they actually look more...

714
00:45:20,712 --> 00:45:23,112
...like hellhounds like this, so it kind of fits.

715
00:45:23,112 --> 00:45:25,112
Yeah! Oh, they're so cute! So cute!

716
00:45:25,512 --> 00:45:26,612
Yeah, give them a big pet.

717
00:45:26,612 --> 00:45:29,712
Yes, yes, good dog! You're a good girl, aren't you?

718
00:45:29,912 --> 00:45:32,512
Yeah, good girl! Good girl!

719
00:45:33,812 --> 00:45:36,612
But wait, why... why are they Dobermans...

720
00:45:36,612 --> 00:45:38,612
...all of a sudden? What happened?

721
00:45:38,812 --> 00:45:41,112
Hahaha! Pokey! Pokey!

722
00:45:41,312 --> 00:45:44,312
Hehehe! Not so fluffy and fuzzy now, hoeh!

723
00:45:44,912 --> 00:45:47,612
Pokey, change us back now!

724
00:45:47,612 --> 00:45:49,612
We can't eat donuts like this!

725
00:45:50,112 --> 00:45:52,612
THAT's why you wanna turn back? Hmph, whatever.

726
00:45:53,012 --> 00:45:56,612
I'll give you one final trial! Clear it...

727
00:45:56,612 --> 00:45:58,612
...and I'll restore them!

728
00:45:58,612 --> 00:46:00,612
Mococo-chan, do this so we can go back to normal!

729
00:46:00,612 --> 00:46:03,112
Okay! Everybody, help us, please!

730
00:46:04,112 --> 00:46:06,612
I... I guess we'll give you one donut for the rescue.

731
00:46:06,612 --> 00:46:10,112
Eh? Just one donut? One each or share it?

732
00:46:10,712 --> 00:46:14,112
Eh? But I kind of like you like this, though.

733
00:46:14,312 --> 00:46:17,512
Well, Pokey, what kind of challenge...

734
00:46:17,512 --> 00:46:19,112
...are you going to give us today?

735
00:46:19,112 --> 00:46:21,112
FUWAMOCO Fukuwarai!

736
00:46:21,112 --> 00:46:23,612
FuwaMoco Fukuwarai? Eh?

737
00:46:23,812 --> 00:46:25,912
Behold, the challenge before you!

738
00:46:26,412 --> 00:46:29,912
Eh? Oh, the carpet has changed! Wow...

739
00:46:29,912 --> 00:46:32,312
...why do they have no faces? That's kind of scary.

740
00:46:32,312 --> 00:46:34,112
Yeah, it is a little freaky. I like it.

741
00:46:34,112 --> 00:46:35,612
Hehe, ever heard of Fukuwarai?

742
00:46:35,612 --> 00:46:39,612
It's this old-school Japanese game —

743
00:46:39,612 --> 00:46:42,612
lemme show you how it's played.

744
00:46:42,612 --> 00:46:45,612
See those two giant faces?

745
00:46:45,612 --> 00:46:48,612
Their face parts are all scattered around.

746
00:46:48,612 --> 00:46:52,112
Bijou and Shiori will be blindfolded...

747
00:46:52,112 --> 00:46:54,112
...and carry the face parts!

748
00:46:54,112 --> 00:46:57,112
Blindfolded? Oh, nice! Oh yeah...

749
00:46:57,112 --> 00:47:00,112
...actually that sounds like fun.

750
00:47:00,112 --> 00:47:01,612
We don't have to do anything.

751
00:47:01,612 --> 00:47:04,612
Big bird, with your words alone, you must guide them.

752
00:47:04,612 --> 00:47:07,612
Lead them to place each piece...

753
00:47:07,612 --> 00:47:09,612
...and restore FUWAMOCO's face!

754
00:47:09,612 --> 00:47:11,112
Me? Yeah, you.

755
00:47:11,112 --> 00:47:14,112
Well, we're just going to be over here blindfolded.

756
00:47:14,112 --> 00:47:16,612
We're just going to chill. Good luck!

757
00:47:16,612 --> 00:47:19,612
Okay, I'll do my best! No pressure! No pressure!

758
00:47:19,612 --> 00:47:21,112
Yeah, it's all up to you!

759
00:47:21,112 --> 00:47:23,112
You've got 5 minutes. Better make it count!

760
00:47:23,112 --> 00:47:26,112
Okay, let's all say FuwaMoco together!

761
00:47:26,112 --> 00:47:28,112
Or not... or not! Let's do this!

762
00:47:28,112 --> 00:47:30,112
Let's go!

763
00:47:31,112 --> 00:47:34,112
All right, ladies. So first plan of action:

764
00:47:34,112 --> 00:47:37,112
Come on over, one on each side of me, pretty please.

765
00:47:37,612 --> 00:47:38,612
Okay.

766
00:47:38,612 --> 00:47:40,612
And then I would like you to turn around.

767
00:47:41,112 --> 00:47:42,112
Oh, okay.

768
00:47:42,612 --> 00:47:46,112
So, I have prepared for you blindfolds,

769
00:47:46,112 --> 00:47:48,612
so I'm going to go ahead and just—

770
00:47:48,612 --> 00:47:51,612
You feel free to adjust them as you'd like, but...

771
00:47:51,612 --> 00:47:54,612
...that way you won't be able to see anything...

772
00:47:54,612 --> 00:47:56,612
...since I have to direct you.

773
00:47:56,612 --> 00:47:58,612
So go ahead and turn back around.

774
00:47:58,612 --> 00:48:00,112
Ha! I cannot see a thing.

775
00:48:00,612 --> 00:48:04,612
Yes, perfect. That's exactly what we want. Aha!

776
00:48:04,612 --> 00:48:08,612
All right, and then we're going to go ahead...

777
00:48:08,612 --> 00:48:11,612
...and start placing these things.

778
00:48:11,612 --> 00:48:14,612
So FuwaMoco, my puppies, I'll do my best for you...

779
00:48:14,612 --> 00:48:17,612
...okay? Do your best, Nerissa! Let's do this!

780
00:48:17,612 --> 00:48:19,612
Let's do it! Woohoo!

781
00:48:19,612 --> 00:48:20,612
Okay, and start!

782
00:48:21,112 --> 00:48:25,112
Okay. So what I'm going to do is...

783
00:48:25,112 --> 00:48:29,112
...I'm going to hand you guys each a piece...

784
00:48:29,112 --> 00:48:31,612
...and then I'm going to tell you where to go.

785
00:48:31,612 --> 00:48:33,112
Who goes first then?

786
00:48:33,112 --> 00:48:36,612
So you're each going to do one face. Okay? Okay.

787
00:48:36,612 --> 00:48:39,612
So, you're going to start that way. Wait, where am I?

788
00:48:39,612 --> 00:48:42,612
Whoa, what? Where am I? What's this?

789
00:48:42,612 --> 00:48:46,112
Shiori's just grabbing...

790
00:48:46,112 --> 00:48:48,112
...I don't know what I just grabbed.

791
00:48:48,112 --> 00:48:51,612
Okay. So, Shiori, walk to me.

792
00:48:51,612 --> 00:48:53,612
Just walk to the sound of my voice.

793
00:48:53,612 --> 00:48:56,612
I'm coming. This is really slow.

794
00:48:56,612 --> 00:48:59,112
Yeah, this way, this way. Walk towards me.

795
00:48:59,112 --> 00:49:01,112
Okay, okay. Walk towards me.

796
00:49:01,112 --> 00:49:03,612
Okay. If I accidentally grab something, I'm sorry.

797
00:49:03,612 --> 00:49:06,112
Okay, grab onto this. This?

798
00:49:06,112 --> 00:49:07,612
Yes.

799
00:49:07,612 --> 00:49:09,612
Okay. Don't move. Okay. Okay.

800
00:49:10,112 --> 00:49:13,612
Don't move! Biboo, I want you to walk...

801
00:49:13,612 --> 00:49:15,612
...to the sound of my voice, okay?

802
00:49:15,612 --> 00:49:17,612
Where is the sound of your voice?

803
00:49:17,612 --> 00:49:20,612
Right here. The sound of my voice!

804
00:49:20,612 --> 00:49:21,612
Where is 'here'?

805
00:49:21,612 --> 00:49:24,612
Right, your right. Your right.

806
00:49:24,612 --> 00:49:26,612
Okay, just a little right.

807
00:49:26,612 --> 00:49:27,612
Okay, forward.

808
00:49:27,612 --> 00:49:29,612
Quickly! Okay, now come to me.

809
00:49:29,612 --> 00:49:31,612
Where is you? Okay.

810
00:49:32,612 --> 00:49:35,612
So, I want you to grab this. Oh, okay, I got it. Yes.

811
00:49:35,612 --> 00:49:39,612
So, pretty much where you are right now...

812
00:49:39,612 --> 00:49:41,612
...not you, Shiori.

813
00:49:41,612 --> 00:49:44,612
Okay, Shiori, come forward a little bit.

814
00:49:44,612 --> 00:49:46,612
This forward or this forward?

815
00:49:46,612 --> 00:49:48,612
The forward towards me. This forward?

816
00:49:48,612 --> 00:49:51,612
Okay, that's too much. Back up just a little bit.

817
00:49:51,612 --> 00:49:54,612
And then I want you to move your right.

818
00:49:54,612 --> 00:49:56,612
Your right. Right? This is right.

819
00:49:56,612 --> 00:49:58,612
Left? Left! Okay, back up.

820
00:49:58,612 --> 00:50:01,612
Oh, Mococo-chan, I don't know...

821
00:50:01,612 --> 00:50:03,612
...if this is going to work out!

822
00:50:03,612 --> 00:50:05,112
Place it down.

823
00:50:05,112 --> 00:50:08,612
I tried to be strong but now I'm regretting that.

824
00:50:08,612 --> 00:50:09,612
Okay. Place it down, Biboo.

825
00:50:09,612 --> 00:50:11,612
Ah, down? Oh, okay.

826
00:50:00,427 --> 00:50:01,427
Move forward a little bit.

827
00:50:01,727 --> 00:50:03,227
Okay, and then can you straighten it out?

828
00:50:03,627 --> 00:50:04,427
Like this?

829
00:50:04,527 --> 00:50:05,927
Yeah, yeah, yeah, just a little bit more.

830
00:50:06,127 --> 00:50:07,127
Like this?

831
00:50:07,527 --> 00:50:09,927
Okay, yeah, and then can you just scoot the whole thing over to the right?

832
00:50:10,127 --> 00:50:11,827
Scoot, scoot, scoot...

833
00:50:11,927 --> 00:50:12,627
No, left.

834
00:50:12,827 --> 00:50:14,127
What about me? Should I do the same?

835
00:50:14,427 --> 00:50:16,727
No, other way! Whoa, whoa, whoa!

836
00:50:19,027 --> 00:50:19,927
What are you doing?

837
00:50:20,127 --> 00:50:22,427
Okay, next items, next items.

838
00:50:23,827 --> 00:50:25,327
Stay right where you are.

839
00:50:25,927 --> 00:50:27,327
Stay right where you are.

840
00:50:27,327 --> 00:50:28,127
I am here where I am.

841
00:50:28,327 --> 00:50:29,427
I'm giving you two, okay?

842
00:50:29,527 --> 00:50:30,327
I got two.

843
00:50:30,427 --> 00:50:32,927
Oh, I don't believe this is happening. Oh!

844
00:50:33,327 --> 00:50:35,427
Oh my god! Nerissa!

845
00:50:36,627 --> 00:50:38,927
Do you have eyes? Ah, ah, ah, do you have eyes?

846
00:50:39,027 --> 00:50:39,627
Yes.

847
00:50:39,727 --> 00:50:41,427
I want you both to walk backwards, okay?

848
00:50:41,527 --> 00:50:42,327
Okay.

849
00:50:42,527 --> 00:50:44,127
Step... maybe straighten out a little bit.

850
00:50:44,127 --> 00:50:46,427
Whoa, that's definitely... okay.

851
00:50:47,127 --> 00:50:48,427
Back... No, actually, you're perfect, Shiori.

852
00:50:49,127 --> 00:50:50,327
You better get running!

853
00:50:50,527 --> 00:50:51,427
I know I'm perfect.

854
00:50:51,627 --> 00:50:52,427
Place... one down.

855
00:50:52,427 --> 00:50:53,127
Which one?

856
00:50:53,127 --> 00:50:53,927
I don't know!

857
00:50:53,927 --> 00:50:54,727
This one!

858
00:50:54,827 --> 00:50:56,427
You're going too far!

859
00:50:56,427 --> 00:50:58,327
This way! Forward again! Forward again!

860
00:50:58,527 --> 00:50:59,627
What? Where do I go?

861
00:50:59,727 --> 00:51:00,627
This way!

862
00:51:00,627 --> 00:51:01,327
It's okay, right?

863
00:51:01,427 --> 00:51:02,927
No! Move it over to the right!

864
00:51:02,927 --> 00:51:05,127
My right? My right? My right?

865
00:51:05,227 --> 00:51:06,427
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah!

866
00:51:06,527 --> 00:51:08,327
I don't think I can do this!

867
00:51:08,627 --> 00:51:10,327
Okay, okay, place the other one down!

868
00:51:10,627 --> 00:51:12,327
I don't want to! I don't want to have to continue like this!

869
00:51:12,527 --> 00:51:13,927
Oh my god! Trust me here!

870
00:51:14,127 --> 00:51:15,427
This way! No, where I am!

871
00:51:15,527 --> 00:51:16,527
This way!

872
00:51:16,627 --> 00:51:18,327
Yeah, our faces have to be like this for real!

873
00:51:18,527 --> 00:51:20,927
Oh my god, Bijou! Okay, Bijou, yeah! Come towards the sound of my voice!

874
00:51:21,127 --> 00:51:23,327
Where is the sound of your voice?!

875
00:51:23,627 --> 00:51:24,927
I think she's over here.

876
00:51:25,127 --> 00:51:27,327
Forward! Forward! Forward!

877
00:51:27,627 --> 00:51:29,327
Okay, stop. Now come this way a little bit.

878
00:51:29,527 --> 00:51:30,927
Turn... this way!

879
00:51:31,027 --> 00:51:31,927
Which way?!

880
00:51:32,027 --> 00:51:33,127
Do you hear where I am?

881
00:51:33,227 --> 00:51:34,127
Oh yes, yes!

882
00:51:34,127 --> 00:51:35,727
Pretend... pretend you're in an immersive game, okay?

883
00:51:35,827 --> 00:51:37,427
Oh yes, I heard... I felt your voice!

884
00:51:37,627 --> 00:51:38,327
Perfect, perfect. Okay, stop, stop, stop.

885
00:51:38,927 --> 00:51:40,127
Okay, now I want you to turn a little bit this way.

886
00:51:40,327 --> 00:51:41,527
Which way? This way?

887
00:51:41,627 --> 00:51:42,927
Wait, sorry, the other way!

888
00:51:43,127 --> 00:51:44,327
Like, rotate your body!

889
00:51:44,327 --> 00:51:45,127
Rotate me!

890
00:51:45,327 --> 00:51:47,427
And this is all wrong! Oh!

891
00:51:47,627 --> 00:51:50,127
Okay, so now I want you to place the one in your left hand down, okay?

892
00:51:50,327 --> 00:51:51,327
On the ground.

893
00:51:51,927 --> 00:51:52,927
Like this?

894
00:51:53,127 --> 00:51:55,327
Yeah, okay. Now I want you to walk slightly in this direction.

895
00:51:55,527 --> 00:51:56,527
Just like, crab walk.

896
00:51:56,627 --> 00:51:57,327
What direction?!

897
00:51:57,327 --> 00:51:58,427
See what ear I'm at?

898
00:51:58,627 --> 00:51:59,327
Oh yes!

899
00:51:59,327 --> 00:52:01,127
Like an immersive game. Feel it like a game, Bijou!

900
00:52:01,227 --> 00:52:02,427
Okay! I'm feeling it!

901
00:52:02,927 --> 00:52:03,927
Okay, place it down.

902
00:52:04,027 --> 00:52:04,927
Like this?

903
00:52:05,027 --> 00:52:05,927
No! Oh no!

904
00:52:06,027 --> 00:52:07,427
I'm doing my best!

905
00:52:08,527 --> 00:52:09,927
Is it done or what?

906
00:52:10,027 --> 00:52:11,327
You have one minute!

907
00:52:11,427 --> 00:52:12,427
One more, okay?

908
00:52:12,527 --> 00:52:13,427
Okay, I'm done.

909
00:52:13,627 --> 00:52:15,427
Okay. Now onto the other one.

910
00:52:16,427 --> 00:52:18,427
So, Bijou, you're... walk this way.

911
00:52:18,527 --> 00:52:20,427
Okay! Which way is this way?

912
00:52:22,127 --> 00:52:23,427
Put it down! Right there!

913
00:52:23,527 --> 00:52:25,327
Wait! No, that's the wrong way! Pick it back up!

914
00:52:27,527 --> 00:52:28,527
Walk... opposite side!

915
00:52:28,627 --> 00:52:29,927
This side?!

916
00:52:30,127 --> 00:52:33,327
Okay! Uh... behind you! Move backwards, backwards, backwards...

917
00:52:33,427 --> 00:52:36,927
backwards, backwards, backwards!

918
00:52:37,127 --> 00:52:38,127
Okay, down!

919
00:52:38,327 --> 00:52:40,427
At least my face looks a bit better than Fuwawa's.

920
00:52:41,127 --> 00:52:42,427
Okay, now walk this way.

921
00:52:42,527 --> 00:52:43,527
Which is this way?

922
00:52:44,027 --> 00:52:45,427
Yeah, yeah. Now walk to your left.

923
00:52:45,527 --> 00:52:47,927
No, no, sorry, right! I think you messed up!

924
00:52:48,027 --> 00:52:48,927
So... sorry!

925
00:52:49,027 --> 00:52:51,427
This way! Left, left, left! This way!

926
00:52:51,527 --> 00:52:52,927
Yes! Okay, now forward.

927
00:52:53,427 --> 00:52:55,127
Forward... yes!

928
00:52:55,227 --> 00:52:56,427
Now put it down!

929
00:52:56,527 --> 00:52:57,727
So good! So good!

930
00:52:57,927 --> 00:52:59,927
Yeah, and then this... please!

931
00:53:00,127 --> 00:53:02,427
No time! 15 seconds left!

932
00:53:02,527 --> 00:53:03,427
Are you done?

933
00:53:03,627 --> 00:53:06,927
Wait, I think I... make it work!

934
00:53:07,027 --> 00:53:08,427
Make it work by brute force!

935
00:53:08,627 --> 00:53:10,427
Yeah, yeah, yeah! 15 seconds!

936
00:53:10,527 --> 00:53:12,927
Don't worry about it! Don't worry about it!

937
00:53:13,027 --> 00:53:14,127
Are we done?

938
00:53:14,227 --> 00:53:15,427
Yeah! One! Done!

939
00:53:17,527 --> 00:53:20,427
Okay, I want you guys to turn on around,

940
00:53:20,527 --> 00:53:22,427
and we're going to take off your blindfolds

941
00:53:22,527 --> 00:53:24,427
so you can see how you did, okay?

942
00:53:24,527 --> 00:53:25,427
Wait, which one's around?

943
00:53:25,527 --> 00:53:26,527
Around?

944
00:53:26,627 --> 00:53:27,527
This way!

945
00:53:32,127 --> 00:53:33,427
Well, let's take a look.

946
00:53:34,027 --> 00:53:35,427
I bet we did great!

947
00:53:35,527 --> 00:53:36,927
There's no way to look at it.

948
00:53:42,627 --> 00:53:44,227
Pokey, what do you think? Isn't it good?

949
00:53:44,327 --> 00:53:47,427
Hey, Bijou, Shiori! You sure this is Fuwawa and Mococo?

950
00:53:48,927 --> 00:53:51,427
Yeah, look at it! Something seems a little...

951
00:53:53,627 --> 00:53:56,427
Nah, nah, nah, it looks great!

952
00:53:56,627 --> 00:53:59,427
It's not upside down or anything!

953
00:53:59,627 --> 00:54:02,427
Wait, can we have a donut please?

954
00:54:02,527 --> 00:54:03,927
I think it looks perfect.

955
00:54:04,127 --> 00:54:05,227
Why are you adjusting it?

956
00:54:05,227 --> 00:54:07,427
I'm not doing anything!

957
00:54:07,527 --> 00:54:09,427
It's not making it better!

958
00:54:14,127 --> 00:54:15,527
